Prosím? Ano, ano.

61
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:10,879
Zasekla se vám karta?

62
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:13,619
Až skončíme tady

63
00:04:13,619 --> 00:04:16,420
a zamíříme k vám, bude to...

64
00:04:18,189 --> 00:04:20,789
Kouknem se. 
Bude to za...

65
00:04:22,929 --> 00:04:25,159
Ale ne!

66
00:04:25,159 --> 00:04:27,599
Ne, paní. Ne.

67
00:04:28,169 --> 00:04:29,270
Paní.

68
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:32,539
- JECOM!
- JECOM!

69
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:38,750
Tak jak se cítíš?

70
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,979
